        description,
        at_higher_level,
        level,
        school,
        range,
        area_size,
        area_shape,
        is_verbal,
        is_somatic,
        materials,
        cast_time,
        duration_type,
        duration,
        effect,
        has_multiple_effects,
        attack_save,
        spell_dice
    )

        $1,
        $2,
        $3,
